'''Patrick Curry''' is an English author. He is the author of ''[[Defending Middle-Earth|Defending Middle-Earth: Tolkien: Myth and Modernity]]'', a book that deals with the ideas of the [[Middle-earth|Middle-Earth]] Universe. Curry has also written on astrology, ethics, and Machiavelli.
